        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">Fire Extinguisher Inspection Costs in Arlington, TX</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Inspection and service costs in the DFW metro area are competitive, with most companies servicing the Arlington, Fort Worth, and Dallas corridor. Here's what to budget:</p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
