            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2">How often do fire extinguishers need to be inspected in Arlington, TX?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Monthly visual checks (by staff), annual professional inspections, 6-year internal examinations, and 12-year hydrostatic testing per NFPA 10 and the City of Arlington Fire Prevention Code.</p>
          </div>
