            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2">How much does a fire extinguisher inspection cost in Arlington, TX?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Annual inspections run $15–$35 per unit in the DFW metro area. 6-year internals cost $25–$55 per unit. 12-year hydrostatic tests cost $30–$75 per unit. Volume discounts available for 20+ units.</p>
          </div>
