            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2">Does Arlington require fire extinguishers in all commercial buildings?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Yes. Arlington adopts the International Fire Code, which requires portable fire extinguishers in all commercial, industrial, and multi-family residential buildings. Type, size, and placement depend on occupancy and hazard classification per NFPA 10.</p>
